--arkanis-- wrote:<BR>Maybe this is not a dev decision as much as an SoE decision.&nbsp; Those expansions were marketed so that if you purchased that expasnion, you got the reward of another race.&nbsp; If they unlock the classes, should they also unlock the 9th spell slot?&nbsp; Because that's also tied to an expansion. Maybe this is unbelievable to you, but there are players that do NOT own the expansions past PoP.&nbsp; Should those people have access to Beserkers?&nbsp; <BR><BR>It's progression, you are meant to go through the content as it was originally presented.&nbsp; Here's a newsflash, races and classes are also considered 'content'. <BR><BR>Tanoril <BR>
